high_descs: Turn around and face the counter to the right of the sink.
Pick the apple up from the counter.
Move to the right and face the microwave.
Put the apple in the microwave and shut the door and turn it on and then open the door and take the apple out and shut the door again.
Move to the right and face the fridge.
Put the apple on the shelf and then close the fridge door.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked apple in the fridge.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the counter to the right of the sink.
Pick up the apple on the counter.
Move to the microwave on your right.
Heat the apple in the microwave.
Move over to the right to the fridge.
Put the microwaved apple in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Put a hot apple in the refrigerator.

high_descs: Turn around and walk forward to the apple on the counter by the sponge.
Pick up the apple from the counter.
Walk forward to the front of the microwave.
Microwave the apple for a few seconds, then take it out and close the microwave.
Turn right and walk to the refrigerator.
Put the apple in the refrigerator, in front of the pan, and close the refrigerator.
anns.task_desc: Put a microwaved apple in a refrigerator.
